title: How Russian Leader Became Key Figure in Global Politics... Again
text: After the 70th UN General Assembly meeting in New York, it has become clear that Russian President Vladimir Putin has managed to break through isolation attempts of Western leaders and come out as a key political leader once again, French newspaper Le Monde said. ...
